they-fall-rich-fury-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/jay-z-getty-images-the-harder-they-fall-rich-fury-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/jay-z-getty-images-the-harder-they-fall-rich-fury-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/jay-z-getty-images-the-harder-they-fall-rich-fury-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/jay-z-getty-images-the-harder-they-fall-rich-fury-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道<a href="/artists/jay-z">，Jay-Z</a>有兴趣收购托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://www.football365.com/news/jay-z-tottenham-takeover-joe-lewis-trial" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Football365</a></em>报道，英国亿万富翁乔·刘易斯（其家族信托基金拥有该足球俱乐部）在对提供内幕交易提示的指控表示无罪后，获得纽约法官的保释。这位 86 岁的老人还面临 16 项安全欺诈罪和 3 项共谋罪。如果这两项罪名成立，刘易斯可能会被判入狱并处以巨额罚款，这意味着他必须放弃对北伦敦俱乐部的所有权。</p><p> Jay-Z 的一位同事告诉<a href="https://www.the-express.com/sport/soccer/106975/Jay-Z-Tottenham-hotspur-bid" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《每日快报》</em></a> ，如果此事成真，这位说唱歌手可能会尝试收购这支橄榄球队。</p><p>他们表示：“那里有不少顶级俱乐部，比如曼联、利物浦和切尔西，现在都归美国所有，杰伊会抓住在热刺全球影响力的董事会层面获得控股权的机会。” 。 “刘易斯先生是否会逍遥法外还有待观察。如果他不这样做，杰伊已经表示，如果他认为价格合适，他希望能够迅速采取行动。” </p><figure id="attachment_3475734" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3475734" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3475734" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jay-z-getty.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jay-z-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jay-z-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jay-z-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jay-z-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jay-z-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jay-z-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="